This api works with nightbot, you will need to add these 3 commands and 1 timer. Nothing else is required. if its the 1st time running the command for the stream duration the server may need to wake up(free service) if iy doesnt respond try again in a few seconds

1️⃣ !spark
Message:
$(urlfetch https://jtracker-50wk.onrender.com/spark?user=$(user))

What it does: Sparks a joint for the user who typed it.


2️⃣ !passj

Message:
$(urlfetch https://jtracker-50wk.onrender.com/pass?from_user=$(user)&to_user=$(query))

What it does: Passes the joint from the user who typed the command to the target user they specify (typed after !passj).


3️⃣ !jointstatus

Message:
$(urlfetch https://jtracker-50wk.onrender.com/status)

What it does: Shows who currently has the joint and how long ago it was passed.


4️⃣ Nightbot Timer

Purpose: Automatically checks the joint for burnout (5-minute timeout).

Message:
$(urlfetch https://jtracker-50wk.onrender.com/status?silent=true)

Interval: 5 minutes
Minimum chat lines: 2 (so it only triggers when chat is active)
